      "Title": "WolverineSoft.DialogueSystem.DialogueManager",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/WolverineSoft.DialogueSystem.DialogueManager.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Primary Component for operating the Backend of the Dialogue System.\nPrimary functions are <xref href=\"WolverineSoft.DialogueSystem.DialogueManager.BeginDialogue(WolverineSoft.DialogueSystem.DialogueAsset%2cSystem.String)\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> and <xref href=\"WolverineSoft.DialogueSystem.DialogueManager.AdvanceDialogue(WolverineSoft.DialogueSystem.AdvanceContext)\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>.\n<xref href=\"WolverineSoft.DialogueSystem.DialogueManager.EndDialogue\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> Is only to be used when ending an interaction prematurely.\nAlso provides interfaces for values and keywords</p>\n"
    },
